{"tid":1539681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［鳩叫］今晚十點 不停大嗌五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:16:27.000Z","uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"afaa24ae32845d13a16cc0ed4e99e099baf6296e","tid":1539681,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:22.000Z","msg":"條柒婆答得嗰一項就以為無咗件事？<br />\n手足隻眼呢？手足條命呢？而家無拎你條命已經執撚到喇 爭取咗幾個月 犧牲咗咁多手足先換得嗰一項<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你當我哋on9?</span></span><br />\n我哋要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可呀</span></span><br />\n唔撚係落吓區 加兩條友就搞掂呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家今晚不斷嗌五大訴求 缺一不可 嗌醒咁多位手足 唔好畀條柒婆呃到呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲諗緊之後出唔出嘅巴絲 睇吓下面嗰幾張相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DP9EwsO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDP9EwsO.png&h=7a25fbd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSg7Fk9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSg7Fk9.jpg&h=5052ebc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edrfPeu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedrfPeu.jpg&h=a8ca7b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2BfPev.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2BfPev.jpg&h=e19daadb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92561007fcba6823603ade3b992a9f597f0fc815","tid":1539681,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:16:27.000Z","msg":"幫推 p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}